Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-35,0:00:-02.-76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-74,0:00:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, dammit, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do we have\Nto be attacked by the navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:02:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to survive this,\Nkeep rowing and stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Give us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got no strength...\NI haven't eaten since this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Major Pasqua! Please\Nreport to the bridge immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Pasqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Pasqua!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have to say so once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're engaging the wanted\Ncriminal Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost missed this historic encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Hand me the binoculars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.\NThat's Straw Hat Luffy's flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dumbass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been firing warning\Nshots at them for a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they've shown no signs of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, if you would do "it," please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It," huh? If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it comes!\NThe major's special technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that has sunk countless\Npirate ships-- the Finger Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What have you done, Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What was that?\N--They shooting at each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, navy rats! I predicted\Nthis would happen from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you predict it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! As their formation collapses,\Nwe'll use this chance to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue the men in the water\Nfrom the sinking ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry is getting farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!\N--There's nothing right about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My chance at a billion\NBerries... no, my promotion...\N--The wheel of fortune is starting to turn, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...is getting away, Major Pasqua!\N--Yeah. Everything is going as history leads it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attend to the wounded! The fleet is\Nsetting course for Luluka, as scheduled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Legend of the Rainbow Mist!\NOld Man Henzo of Luluka Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we gave them the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been chasing us pretty hard lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there are two people with\Nprices on their heads aboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't blame the navy for going all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nico Robin 79 million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monkey D. Luffy\N30 million Berries\N(actually 100 million Berries)"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roronoa Zoro\N(actually 60 million Berries)"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch yourself. It looks like there are\Nlots of hidden reefs under the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's a harbor!\N--What?! A harbor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! You can see the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A harbor, huh? Which means\Nthere'll be something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not a lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is a tall tower, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Let's go get\Nsome food to eat! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Just wipe off that drool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the island of Luluka,\Nall ships that moor at our harbor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even along our rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must pay harbor dues!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harbor dues?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, we have to pay them money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why should we have to\Npay a tax just for docking here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's your duty! Will you pay, or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that to a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! Food! Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm completely fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go. I want to get some\Nblank charts to draw some maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--J-Just a minute! I'm coming, too! Me too!\N--Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new kind of clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a swindling salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen a rainbow-colored mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Rainbow-colored mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's no use. He's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're labeling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of attitude is that,\Nafter asking me a question?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you might tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, hit me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up! One more special!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got money for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you the secrets of the\NRainbow Mist. Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Henzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a genius, repeat, genius scientist\Nresearching the Rainbow Mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call yourself a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who calls themselves\Nthat is no honest fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Henzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "professor."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, do you know this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came across it in Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it. I thought I heard about\Nthe Rainbow Mist somewhere before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it turns out it's the name of\Nthe book you're reading, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the author is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the book was written over 40 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the book, the Rainbow\NMist is the garden of the gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps El Dorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's recorded as being the\Nentrance to the City of Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing more than a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many adventurers have\Nbeen enticed by the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set off on a journey\Nto find the Rainbow Mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not a single one of them has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, including my own friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're researching the mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best not take what\Nhe has to say at face value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of Mayor Wetton's dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He receives research\Nfunding from the mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lives the easy life! He's a flimflam scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The tax collection squad!\NThe tax collection squad is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--Hey, hurry and drink that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, good citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you having an enjoyable mealtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, you're drinking\Nsome delicious liquor, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you drink liquor, you need to\Npay the liquor-drinking tax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All I've got in my wallet is my\Nwife and kids' living expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a citizen's obligation to pay taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who neglect their obligations\Nhave no right to live in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor Wetton's son, Flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A disagreeable bastard, who extorts\Nall sorts of tax money out of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, Professor Henzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was wondering how\Nyour mist research is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling when or where\Nthe mist is going to appear, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. Your research is supported\Nby the citizens' tax money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Tower over there was\Nconstructed based on your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not forget that the\Nslower your research goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more it puts everyone here out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I will see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, you're eating a\Nheaping plate of spaghetti, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm, I was hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating a heaping plate means that\Nyou must pay a heaping tax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, for pete's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aah, thanks.\N--Cram it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want the people\Nin town to think ill of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then stop hanging around with Henzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not up to me to decide.\NIt's up to the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you still shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to buy some blank charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we run out while we're\Nat sea, we'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are buying a lot of\Nunrelated stuff, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, I'd follow you into the\Ndepths of hell to go shopping with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are, Lake-sama! They're the ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the insolent folks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't pay their taxes\Nat the harbor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mayor Wetton's grandson, Lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the officer who seizes\Nunpaid taxes from the insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly sure what's going on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're here to throw cold water\Non our enjoyable little shopping trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The moment I touched\Nhis body, I got a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. That's what happens\Nto everyone who touches me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Electricity?\N--I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the abilities of a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your own private generator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dynamo Squad, increase output!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, this doesn't look good, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good taste of the power\Nof my electroshock suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was that thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely dodged. But that\Nwon't happen this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, look after Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, don't do anything reckless, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh, those are what I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Not only will they not\Nget hurt, they won't even get dusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a real outrageous mayor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He takes money from everywhere,\Nand says it's for taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does he get off calling it\Na heaping tax? What a rip-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you apologizing for, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you listen to what\Nthose guys were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Pops here is in league\Nwith those rip-off artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's money is being wasted,\Non account of his weird research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nope, not a bit.\N--Look, Luffy, you've got your snails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nope, not at all.\N--Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ship! A galleon is arriving in the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A galleon?\N--I-It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting! Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite an old ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Talielisin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tali--? W-What? H-Hey, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slick! Awesome! I want one! I totally want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, knowing you, I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji!\N--Shopping bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's just stupid... I dodged it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the stupid one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, it's the metal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The valuables are drawing\Nthe electricity! Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what will happen\Nif you drop them, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... after taking an\Nelectric current as strong as that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a normal person would already be--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not normal, so no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... If my striking attacks\Nare completely useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's running!\N--Hey, hold it!\N--Ah, Lake-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold on to my shopping bags tight!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're that important, why\Ndon't you carry them yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that wrong?\N--No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui! Isoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo! Pukau!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, let me have that boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You ate a Devil Fruit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm a rubber man,\Nwho ate the Gum-Gum Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you have that machine, the H-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't say that, let me have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there were people\Nhere just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single person\Nanywhere on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is one that went adrift 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hard time believing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is just as it was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what are you talking about, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My radar is reacting! I've never\Nhad a reading this strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't go out into the open\Nsea in the H-1! What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm borrowing this!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go stealing our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna go, take the galleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Talielisin's helm is still\Nbroken, by Wetton's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean, Pops?\NHow do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because 50 years ago,\NI was aboard the Talielisin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's gone!\N--The Going Merry is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys from earlier must\Nhave taken it, in place of the tax!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it's at the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that mossy bastard is good for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we really going in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a place many\Nadventures have challenged,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but none have ever returned from, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reason why I've kept\Nup my research through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No way am I scared! I am he\Nwho travels all over the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're charging into the Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert? It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship graveyard, where once\Nyou enter, you can never get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once a pirate, just like you are.\NI'm not afraid of a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, a pirate? Doesn't look like it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, I firmly\Nbelieved that I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that young pirate still\Nlives on, inside your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your story, old-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Residents of the Land of Eternity!\NThe Pumpkin Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
